name: Unlucky Cheaters
description:
Professor Kyle gives two forms of his tests to deter cheaters, however some of his students don't know this and copy answers off the wrong form! Help him analyse the {{url_for("studentdata.dat", display="test data")}} and find the cheaters.
Note: Submit the last names of the cheaters in alphabetical order, separated only by commas.
hints: Statistically, you should probably be at least 99.98% confident.
author: Michael
